#. type: multicols*
#: sections/recommendations.tex:12
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\subsection*{Play Time}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/recommendations.tex:14
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"You can estimate your \\textbf{minimal} play time using the following formula:\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/recommendations.tex:18
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\begin{center}\n"
"  Play Time $= \\boldsymbol{P × R × 5}$ [min]\n"
"\\end{center}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/recommendations.tex:24
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Where:\n"
"\\begin{itemize}\n"
"  \\item[$\\textbf{P}$] -- number of players\n"
"  \\item[$\\textbf{R}$] -- number of Rounds\n"
"\\end{itemize}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/recommendations.tex:27
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"For example, if you're playing a 3-player Scenario consisting of 12 Rounds, you can easily calculate that $3 \\times 12 \\times 5 = 180$.\n"
"Your expected minimal play time would be around 3 hours.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/recommendations.tex:30
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"To calculate the \\textbf{upper bound} of your play time (more realistic if there are inexperienced players), simply double the result.\n"
"In this case, that would be 6 hours.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/recommendations.tex:32
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\subsection*{Magic Arrows}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/recommendations.tex:35
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Except for the Magic Arrow, each Spell appears exactly twice in the Spell Deck.\n"
"After players prepare their starting M\\&M Decks, it is recommended to remove Magic Arrows from the Spell Deck until no more than two remain.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

